@startuml UC-09_Explore_Marketplace

title UC-09: Explore Marketplace - Sequence Diagram

skinparam SequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam SequenceArrowColor #6A1B9A
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #F3E5F5
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF

actor User
participant Frontend
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant MarketplaceService
participant Database as DB

User -> Frontend: 1. Click Marketplace
Frontend -> API: 2. GET /api/v1/marketplace/items?category=templates&page=1
API -> MarketplaceService: 3. list_marketplace_items(category, page, filters)
MarketplaceService -> DB: 4. Query marketplace_collection
DB --> MarketplaceService: 5. Items paginated
MarketplaceService -> DB: 6. Fetch item ratings & reviews
DB --> MarketplaceService: 7. Rating data
MarketplaceService --> API: 8. Return {items[], pagination, filters}
API --> Frontend: 9. 200 OK + marketplace data
Frontend --> User: 10. Display marketplace grid

User -> Frontend: 11. Search for "email"
Frontend -> API: 12. GET /api/v1/marketplace/search?q=email&filters=...
API -> MarketplaceService: 13. search_marketplace(query, filters)
MarketplaceService -> DB: 14. Full-text search
DB --> MarketplaceService: 15. Search results
MarketplaceService --> API: 16. Return results
API --> Frontend: 17. 200 OK + search results
Frontend --> User: 18. Display filtered results

@enduml
